description:
Danny talks to Toya Bush-Harris from Bravo's Married to Medicine about her current relationship with the women, the hair/makeup payment debacle, and lots more! Then Danny sits down with Ryan O'Connell to discuss season 2 of his show Special on Netflix. They also dive into the world of Bravo, 90210, disability representation, and lots more!


Toya Bush Harris Interview: 2:00ish

Ryan O'Connell Interview: 21:53ish
